window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>At the gates between worlds... </p> <p>In a war outside of time... </p> <p>He fights for us. </p> <p>Reclusive college student Jonathan Tibbs wakes in a pool of blood, not a scratch on him. His life is about to undergo a massive shift. A violent and merciless otherworldly enemy unleashes slaughter in the streets, calling out in a language only he understands. </p> <p>And it is seeking its challenger. </p> <p>In order to defeat the threat, Jonathan must become a temporal weapon...while remaining completely anonymous. Unfortunately, harnessing off-world powers has its own special challenges... </p> <p><i>The Never Hero</i> is the first installment in The Chronicles of Jonathan Tibbs - a mind-bending, genre-crossing action-adventure trilogy. </p>"; 
